{"tid":1174682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（Now新聞）德駐港總領事：德外交部無參與難民審批","createTime":"2019-05-28T04:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T04:43:56.000Z","uid":36494,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c59bc889be9a00544226fc37201d8c3a928f485","tid":1174682,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"德國駐港總領事館發新聞稿，回應行政長官林鄭月娥早前就黃台仰及李東昇獲批難民庇護的關注，指德國聯邦移民及難民署依法審批難民申請，德國外交部並無參與。 <br />\n<br />\n德國駐港總領事館指，德國聯邦政府十分重視與特區政府傳統上非常良好的雙邊關係，重申德國政府對港政策不變，未來亦會繼續促進雙邊關係。<br />\n<br />\n至於有兩名港人對傳媒稱於德國獲批難民身分，領事館因私隱問題不會評論個別個案，又指德國聯邦移民及難民署在審批庇護申請時，會考慮當事人在會面所提出的理據，每宗申請都是依法審批，德國外交部並無參與決策過程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係話俾支那知<br />\n支那唔好諗住外交壓力會影響德國審批難民的決定"},{"pid":"a6dc7982f04f571bb3e4cb8f0ea6fa484623e6b9","tid":1174682,"uid":3976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada501212e15c1945692bdb777b4f5ba60755886","tid":1174682,"uid":68463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"領事館因私隱問題不會評論個別個案<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ddfd8dadda86b17c5f4394effffe40157ef328","tid":1174682,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"德駐港總領事：德外交部無參與難民審批<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=349585&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349585%26refer%3DShare&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=d338fe3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349585%26refer%3DShare&h=a2693b1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=349585&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNow新聞片"},{"pid":"1565f015f8930c3652745e3bf2d0a633eb4b591a","tid":1174682,